Name: Stickman go
About the game: “Stickman go” is a puzzle game based on physics engine. Click red item to break it and in the mean time stickman will be affected by other items' block, drag, or gravity effect. Final goal of player is moving stickman out of screen, in this process, you may find some retarded physical phenomena. XD
